                             THE TEXT WINDOW

THE TEXT WINDOW TO THE RIGHT OF THE ICON DRIVER IS WHERE ALL COMMANDS YOU 
ISSUE WILL BE PRINTED, AND WHERE YOU WILL BE PRESENTED WITH THE RESULT OF THE
ACTION IN THE FORM OF TEXT. THE WAY THAT THE COMPUTER DOES THIS IS BY USING
WHAT IS KNOWN AS A `PARSER` WHICH INTERPERTS YOUR COMMANDS,ORIGINALLY,PARSERS
WERE VERY SIMPLE AND RUDIMENTERY, BUT THINGS HAVE MOVED ON, AND THE PARSER IN
SUSPICIOUS CARGO IS A FULLY-FEATURED MULTIPLE SENTENCE ANALYSER WHICH ACCEPTS
COMMANDS IN ENGLISH SENTENCES.EACH SENTENCE MUST HAVE A VERB(OR ACTION) AND
MUST BE SIMILAR TO AN ENGLISH COMMAND, SUCH AS `take the credit card`
`eat the greasy hamburger`, put the ming vase in the smelly sack` `ask the old
stooping man for a dime`.
SENTENCES CAN BE SEPERATED USING THE STANDARD FULL STOP,COMMA OR SEMI-COLON.
THE PARSER WILL UNDERSTAND FAR MORE COMMANDS THAN THE ICON DRIVER, BUT IT
SHOULD BE NOTED THAT ALL COMMANDS TO COMPLETE THE GAME ARE AVAILABLE ON THE
ICON DRIVER. PRONOUNS(IT,THEM,ect) PLURALS AND PREPOSITIONS(IN,FORM) ARE ALL
ACCEPTED AND UNDERSTOOD.IN ADDITION SPEECH,EXCEPTIONS AND POSITIONAL 
REFERENCES ARE ACCEPTED.

CONVERSING WITH OTHER CHARACTERS
--------------------------------
CONVERSATION IS GENERALLY HANDLED BY USING ONE OF THE FOLLOWING TWO PHRASES.

ASK PERSON ABOUT (or FOR) SOMETHING
TELL PERSON ABOUT SOMETHING

OTHER WORDS CAN BE USED,BUT IF YOU STICK TO THE ABOVE 2 METHODS OF PHRASING,
THE CHANCES ARE YOU WILL BE UNDERSTOOD EVERY TIME. IN CERTAIN CASES YOU MAY 
NOT BE SPECIFIC ENOUGH ABOUT AN ITEM, IN WHICH YOU WILL BE PROMPTED FOR MORE
INFO. IF THERE ARE 2 PENCILS,FOR EXAMPLE, A BLUE AND A GREEN, THEN TYPING;

get pencil (IS NOT SPECIFIC ENOUGH AND YOU WOULD BE PROMPTED)

which one the blue pencil? or the green pencil? 9TO WHICH YOU WOULD TYPE)

THE BLUE PENCIL /OR BLUE / OR BLUE PENCIL

YOU MAY ALSO BE ASKED: with what?
                       what do you want me to put the item in?

AGAIN, THESE QUESTIONS SHOULD BE ANSWERED BY TYPING IN THE APPROPRIATE ANSWER.
IF YOU WANT TO CARRY ON, YOU CAN IGNORE THE QUESTION AND TYPE ANOTHER SENTENCE

THERE ARE A NUMBER OF EDITING COMMANDS, ALL OF WHICH ARE LISTED, AT THE END OF
