LANDER
------
THE LANDER HAS 2 STAGES, LANDING ON THE MOON, AND RETURNING TO THE SHIP. BOTH
STAGES ARE ESSENTIALLY THE SAME, EXCEPT FOR THE DIRECTION OF TRAVEL. ON
LANDING THE SHUTTLE MUST BE VERTICAL, NOSE TO THE TOP OF THE SCREEN AND MUST
HAVE A LOW VELOCITY. ON RETURN, THE SHUTTLE MUST REACH THE TARGET CROSSHAIR
WHICH WILL APPEAR ON THE SCREEN.

THE KEYS ARE;  Z      ROTATE LEFT
               X      ROTATE RIGHT
               SHIFT  THRUST
               P      PAUSE
               ESC    BYPASS THE LANDER GAME
